headline: Dave & Buster's (PLAY) Misses Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Dave & Buster's (PLAY) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -54.55% and -0.81%, respectively, for the quarter ended July 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
